===Adjective===
'''monotonic'''

# of or using the Greek system of [[diacritic]]s which discards the [[breathing]]s and employs a single accent to indicate stress.
# (''Mathematics'') said of a function that either never decreases or never increases as its [[independent variable]] increases.

====Antonym====
*(1): [[polytonic]]

